so I looked into it. A backup plan.

570
00:32:23,691 --> 00:32:25,526
How many of those do you have?

571
00:32:26,277 --> 00:32:29,489
Do you just drive around
making mental notes

572
00:32:29,572 --> 00:32:32,784
