676
00:38:55,750 --> 00:38:58,711
Having someone on my... team.

677
00:39:00,963 --> 00:39:01,797
Yeah.

678
00:39:02,423 --> 00:39:04,175
Yeah, that sounds nice.

679
00:39:08,512 --> 00:39:09,764
