704
00:40:43,858 --> 00:40:46,694
The girl-- The woman I fell in love with.

705
00:40:47,820 --> 00:40:53,826
Warm, playful, honest,
and beautifully, radiantly maternal.

706
00:40:55,661 --> 00:40:59,331
