711
00:41:10,551 --> 00:41:11,886
It's not just him.

712
00:41:13,929 --> 00:41:15,514
It's not just our son.

713
00:41:18,225 --> 00:41:19,768
[upbeat music playing]

714
00:41:23,689 --> 00:41:25,191
